[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      2[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      3[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Complexity:** Complex · **Phase:** Production · **Estimated Cost:** ~$1,200–$5,000 per month per regional surveillance workload
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      4[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
